## Details

<details>
    <summary>Why serve through a window at night?</summary>
    It is important to note that for security reasons, many duty pharmacies close their main door at night and serve you through a secure window. Don't hesitate to ring the bell if no one is at the counter!
</details>

> In summary: The duty system is a chain of solidarity among pharmacists to ensure you never lack care. The next time you have a nighttime emergency, don't panic, don't take your car at random: make it a habit to check online which duty pharmacy is open in your neighborhood.

